## Environment Variable Reference

| Variable | Where to Get | Notes |
|----------|--------------|-------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase Dashboard > Settings > API | Public — safe for client-side |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` | Supabase Dashboard > Settings > API | Public — safe for client-side |
| `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` | Supabase Dashboard > Settings > API | **Secret** — never expose to client |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` | Google Cloud Console > Credentials | **Secret** — keep in server env only |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Google Cloud Console > Credentials | **Secret** — keep in server env only |
| `APPLE_CLIENT_ID` | Apple Developer Portal > Services IDs | The Services ID string |
| `APPLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Generated from `.p8` key | **Expires in 6 months** — set rotation reminder |
